Wow. The uploader must be on crack or something to upload this. Swap Magic's purpose is to enable booting of backups. Since this is not an original Sony pressed disc, you'll need to use some kind of mod to boot this anyways. DON'T WASTE YOUR TIME PEOPLE!!!! THIS WILL NOT WORK. If your PS2 is not modded, there's no way to boot this. If it is, well then, you don't need this in the first place anyways.
